This directory is for bundled native libraries.

## Required: pdfium.dll

Place the Pdfium shared library for Windows here:

- `resources/lib/pdfium.dll` — Windows x86_64

### Where to get pdfium.dll

Download from the [pdfium-render releases](https://github.com/ajrcarey/pdfium-render/releases)
or build from the [Google Pdfium source](https://pdfium.googlesource.com/pdfium/).

The DLL version must be compatible with the `pdfium-render` crate version in
`Cargo.toml`. Check the crate's README for the recommended Pdfium binary version.

### Other platforms

- Linux: `libpdfium.so` (place alongside this directory or install system-wide)
- macOS: `libpdfium.dylib` (place alongside this directory or install system-wide)

### Resolution order

1. **Bundled**: `resources/lib/pdfium.dll` (via Tauri's BaseDirectory::Resource)
2. **Development**: `CARGO_MANIFEST_DIR/resources/lib/pdfium.dll`
3. **System library**: OS default search paths (PATH, /usr/lib, etc.)

See `src/ocr/pdf.rs` for the implementation.